ion, and saturate at unity only as the lattice is completely smoothed\nout.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Jan 2013 19:09:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 15 Oct 2013 18:30:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-12"}
