ian, and this allows us\nto compute its values knowing them only on objects on the rim of the quiver.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 20 Jan 2013 22:28:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 2 Jun 2023 04:21:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-06-05"}
